Create a new issue in this repository through this link:

The model generator works best with simple objects, i.e 'a motorcycle', 'an airplane', or 'a laptop'.

3DREADME first leverages GitHub's Webhooks and Issues to receive a text prompt from the user (you!). We then utilize a tweaked version OpenAI's Point-E model to generate a point-cloud field that represents the described object.
